# Empyrebase

A simple python wrapper for the [Firebase API](https://firebase.google.com). Supports Realtime DB, Firestore, Auth and Storage.
<p align="center">
<img src="images/empyrebase-logo.png" alt="Empyrebase logo" width="200"/>
</p>

